cc20.description: 20. During the past 7 days, on how many days did you engage in vigorous physical activities such as heavy lifting, digging, aerobics, or fast cycling?

cc21_a.description: 21. How long in total did it usually take you to do vigorous physical activities on one of those days you did them? Hours per days

cc21_b.description: 21. How long in total did it usually take you to do vigorous physical activities on one of those days you did them? Minutes per day

cc22.description: 22. During the past 7 days, on how many days did you do moderate physical activities such as carrying light objects or riding a bike at a steady pace? Do not include walks.

cc23_a.description: 23. Usually, how much time do you spend on one of those days doing moderate physical activities? Hours per day

cc23_b.description: 23. Usually, how much time do you spend on one of those days doing moderate physical activities? Minutes per day

cc24.description: 24. During the past 7 days, on how many days did you walk for at least 10 continuous minutes?

cc25_a.description: 25. Usually, how much time did you spend on one of those days walking? Hours per day

cc25_b.description: 25. Usually, how much time did you spend on one of those days walking? Minutes per day

cc26_a.description: 26. During the last 7 days, how long did you sit on one day of the week?
